{"sections":[],"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView(im)setTargetCoordinate:animated:","role":"symbol","platforms":[],"symbolKind":"method","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setTargetCoordinate:animated:"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setTargetCoordinate:animated:"}],"remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapView.h#L775","fileName":"MLNMapView.h"},"title":"setTargetCoordinate:animated:","roleHeading":"Instance Method"},"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/settargetcoordinate:animated:"]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS","iPadOS","Mac Catalyst"],"tokens":[{"text":"- (","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:v","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"void"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setTargetCoordinate:"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"CLLocationCoordinate2D","preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@CLLocationCoordinate2D","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"targetCoordinate"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"animated:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"BOOL","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"text":"animated","kind":"internalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"targetCoordinate","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The target coordinate to fit within the viewport."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"If ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"YES"},{"text":", the map animates to fit the target within the map","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"view. If ","type":"text"},{"code":"NO","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", the map fits the target instantaneously."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"animated"}]},{"content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","level":2,"anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"By default, the target coordinate is set to an invalid coordinate, indicating","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"that there is no target. In course tracking mode, the target forms one of two"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"foci in the viewport, the other being the user location annotation. Typically,"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the target is set to a destination or waypoint in a real-time navigation scene.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"As the user annotation moves toward the target, the map automatically zooms in","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"to fit both foci optimally within the viewport.","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"This method has no effect if the ","type":"text"},{"code":"userTrackingMode","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" property is set to a value","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"other than "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserTrackingMode\/MLNUserTrackingModeFollowWithCourse"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"To specify a completion handler to execute after the animation finishes, use","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the ","type":"text"},{"code":"-setTargetCoordinate:animated:completionHandler:","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" method.","type":"text"}]}],"kind":"content"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"]]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Deprecat